Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.15,0:00:25.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.15,0:00:29.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Evening! What's up, Senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.28,0:00:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.92,0:00:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.40,0:00:35.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry this is out of the blue, Uzaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.61,0:00:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,,What is?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.03,0:00:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Please: be with me. I need you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.32,0:00:43.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.40,0:02:24.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Please: be with me. I need you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.65,0:02:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.28,0:02:32.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.15,0:02:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.90,0:02:36.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry. I know this is sudden.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.03,0:02:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.28,0:02:42.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, you asked me to be with you?\NOn the phone?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.57,0:02:46.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, about that...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.78,0:02:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.86,0:02:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I just can't seem\Nto bring myself to go in alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.40,0:02:57.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Come with me to the cat café!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.03,0:03:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank God you're here! I mean it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.86,0:03:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, wow, I can't wait!\NThis is my first time--I'm so nervous!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.94,0:03:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow! What--hey! Quit kicking--ow!\NStop! Cut it out! That hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.32,0:03:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Party of two?\NTake off your shoes and go on inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.48,0:03:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow... cats!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.90,0:03:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,They have cats, Uzaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.32,0:03:34.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep. They have cats, all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.73,0:03:37.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, duh. We {\i1}are{\i0} a cat café.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.15,0:03:41.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I... I can touch them, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.61,0:03:45.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Calm down, Senpai. You've got those scary eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.23,0:03:49.57,Default,,0,0,0,,If the cats are okay with it,\Ngo right ahead and pet them gently.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.57,0:03:51.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.61,0:03:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Do it like I taught you earlier: from below.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.90,0:03:57.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.11,0:04:00.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.78,0:04:05.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Now's your chance! Cats like being scratched\Nunder their chins or behind their ears.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.53,0:04:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.69,0:04:20.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Uzaki, look! A cat--on my lap!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.07,0:04:21.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, yes. Good for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.98,0:04:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,But don't be too loud, or it'll run away.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.03,0:04:30.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow. Creepy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.07,0:04:33.53,Default,,0,0,0,,He doesn't get this excited around humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.53,0:04:37.57,Default,,0,0,0,,All that gloominess must be\Nkeeping some stuff repressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.57,0:04:39.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Cootchie, cootchie, coo...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.57,0:04:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,He's so creepy that I don't even mind\Nthe {\i1}extremely{\i0} misleading way
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.03,0:04:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,he got me here in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.82,0:04:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,He's too overjoyed for words.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.36,0:04:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Uzaki, what's with that plastered-on smile?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.36,0:04:58.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Just thinking how creepy it is that\Nyou act so cool, but you like cute things.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.32,0:04:59.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Say what? Jerk.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.48,0:05:01.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoops. My true feelings slipped out.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.15,0:05:02.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.69,0:05:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It's {\i1}also{\i0} creepy that you're careful\Nto speak quietly so as not to spook the cats.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.36,0:05:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Figures!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.40,0:05:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, your true feelings are showing again.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.03,0:05:18.44,Default,,0,0,0,,But I {\i1}am{\i0} glad you came today.\NI'd get to the entrance and do a U-turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.44,0:05:20.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You're exaggerating.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.07,0:05:22.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got to thank you somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.23,0:05:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.32,0:05:25.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Anything come to mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.15,0:05:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm... let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.19,0:05:32.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, my birthday's actually coming up soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.98,0:05:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm turning 20, so I'd like to make it sorta special.{maybe we should add that turning 20 is considered to be an adult in japan}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.78,0:05:38.82,Default,,0,0,0,,So, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.82,0:05:40.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Uzaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.73,0:05:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.44,0:05:44.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Truth is...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.65,0:05:47.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.23,0:05:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,My legs are so numb that\NI haven't processed anything you've said.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.07,0:05:53.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you repeat that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.65,0:05:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Then get rid of the cat!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.78,0:05:57.32,Default,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.32,0:05:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,If you can't have a conversation,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.40,0:06:01.19,Default,,0,0,0,,we'll just move it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.19,0:06:04.57,Default,,0,0,0,,But it was finally on my lap!\NJust a little longer?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.57,0:06:07.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Uncross your legs already\Nand get those pins and needles out.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.69,0:06:10.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not a quick-fix kind of thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.19,0:06:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow, ow, ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.36,0:06:13.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.15,0:06:19.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Poke!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.61,0:06:21.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Cut that out! What the hell? Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.61,0:06:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You were just {\i1}so{\i0} wide open,\Nyou were practically {\i1}asking{\i0} for it!{that was gold puahahah - aria}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.36,0:06:34.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, right! {\i1}Everybody's{\i0} wide open\Nwhen their legs are numb!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.11,0:06:39.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Not so loud, now--you'll scare the kitty-cats!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.86,0:06:44.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Poke!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.61,0:06:46.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Pokety poke!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.94,0:06:49.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Pokety, pokety poke-poke-poke!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.69,0:06:53.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Pokety, pokety, pokety, pokety poke!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.86,0:06:56.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, jeez, what now? This is really fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.61,0:06:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,This might just awaken something in me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.48,0:07:03.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Uzaki... please... uncle...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.53,0:07:07.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm? I can't hear you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.11,0:07:10.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What color is your blood?!{this is so literal, "I'll bathe in your blood" I'd say}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.82,0:07:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Save that kind of play for home, please.{ew buzzkill}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.36,0:07:15.65,Default,,0,0,0,,"Play"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.90,0:07:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Phew, what a blast!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.28,0:07:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Wasn't that fun, Senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.82,0:07:26.65,Default,,0,0,0,,The first half was. Then {\i1}you{\i0} got us thrown out!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.65,0:07:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit. Next time I'll go alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.40,0:07:32.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Probably can't go back there, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.23,0:07:33.65,Default,,0,0,0,,And whose fault is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.65,0:07:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Gotta love cat cafés, though.\NLots of friendly kitties!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.86,0:07:41.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Right? They were so used to being around people.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.78,0:07:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Very Easy Mode.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.36,0:07:47.32,Default,,0,0,0,,"Your communication level is puny.\NLevel 5? Too bad."{not "too bad" but "what a trash" or "fucking noob" for the max lulz}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.32,0:07:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,And they still warmed up to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.90,0:07:52.28,Default,,0,0,0,,So I'm a gun-toting old man now?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.28,0:07:56.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I have cats at home, but it's good\Nto interact with different cats sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.57,0:07:59.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh! Must be nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.23,0:08:03.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this what married men\Nwho go to cabaret clubs feel like?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.11,0:08:06.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Beats me! What a horrible analogy.{"I wholeheatedly hate this analogy"}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.53,0:08:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,See you later, Senpai!{"good work out there, Sakurai"}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.73,0:08:13.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep. I owe you one for today,\Nso think it over, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.53,0:08:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I've already thought {\i1}that{\i0} over.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.48,0:08:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,And?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.32,0:08:22.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Like I mentioned earlier,\Nmy birthday is coming up. August 7th!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.73,0:08:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I have high hopes, Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.82,0:08:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Her birthday...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.78,0:08:32.19,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.19,0:08:35.78,Default,,0,0,0,,...she said she has high hopes for her birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.78,0:08:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're in a pickle.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.86,0:08:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You {\i1}do{\i0} seem like you'd\Nbe bad at that kind of thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.40,0:08:41.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.48,0:08:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Anticipating that Sakurai would be bad at this,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.40,0:08:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,then throwing him for a loop\Nwith vague "high hopes"...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.32,0:08:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,She's quite the schemer.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.36,0:08:53.53,Default,,0,0,0,,But that comes from the\Npeculiar mentality of a girl in love
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.53,0:08:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,who wants someone to fret over her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.40,0:08:59.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Not that Hana realizes it herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.36,0:09:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, any way you look at it...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.28,0:09:03.69,Default,,0,0,0,,...we're going to eat this up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.69,0:09:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.78,0:09:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.69,0:09:09.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have any ideas?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.03,0:09:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been thinking...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.32,0:09:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,U-Uzaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.98,0:09:18.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Flowers, because my name means "flower"?\NSo you suck at puns, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.98,0:09:20.57,Default,,0,0,0,,U-Uzaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.57,0:09:22.61,Default,,0,0,0,,This is totally the wrong size!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.61,0:09:28.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, only hotties can get away\Nwith giving a present like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.07,0:09:29.86,Default,,0,0,0,,U-Uzaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.86,0:09:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Couldn't you have given me\Na uTunes card instead?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.32,0:09:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I want those special-event bonuses!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.90,0:09:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It feels like anything\NI give her will be a bust.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.28,0:09:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,This is getting complicated!{same as the old one, "he is making this complicated"}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.82,0:09:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,In reality...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.23,0:09:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,He sure doesn't have an eye for flowers.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.98,0:09:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,A placeholder!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.44,0:10:00.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, it has multiplayer!\NI'll play with you, loner senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.61,0:10:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds about right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.48,0:10:07.61,Default,,0,0,0,,She'd be happy with anything Sakurai gives her.{"There is no way she'd be happy"}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.61,0:10:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I've thought about this\Ntoo much--I'm just so confused.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.78,0:10:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Then why don't you follow your intuition?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.86,0:10:15.07,Default,,0,0,0,,My intuition?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.07,0:10:19.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Give her the first thing that came\Nto mind when you heard "birthday present."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.53,0:10:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,The first thing that came to mind...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.15,0:10:30.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I still have no idea.{That's what she told me, but I still have no idea"}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.23,0:10:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,But I need to pick something today.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.23,0:10:39.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What's up, Uzaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.82,0:10:42.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.28,0:10:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.90,0:10:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I know this is sudden, Senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.57,0:10:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What is?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.86,0:10:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I want you to be with me! I need you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.28,0:10:55.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.19,0:11:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I want you to be with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.48,0:11:04.19,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with Uzaki, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.19,0:11:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.32,0:11:12.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\pos(949.5,160.5)\c&H758EC9&\3c&H758EC9&}Pub
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.82,0:11:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.48,0:11:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.28,0:11:13.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry to spring this on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.07,0:11:14.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.98,0:11:20.53,Default,,0,0,0,,So, um, on the phone...\Nyou said you wanted me to be with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.32,0:11:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,About that...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.65,0:11:29.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I just couldn't bring myself to go in alone!\NCome with me, Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.73,0:11:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,A... pub?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.90,0:11:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Your treat! Please?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.48,0:11:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What for?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.48,0:11:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you, remember? My 20th birthday!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.11,0:11:41.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I have high hopes, you know--
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.86,0:11:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,for your wallet, that is!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.19,0:11:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,"High hopes"--you mean you were\Nangling for a pub visit all along?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.48,0:11:50.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.86,0:11:55.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What's wrong? C'mon, let's go in already!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.32,0:11:59.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.90,0:12:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.94,0:12:08.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Celebrating your milestone 20th at a pub?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.19,0:12:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, totally! I wanted to try drinking with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.61,0:12:15.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Drinking's fun, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.11,0:12:18.73,Default,,0,0,0,,That depends on the drinker,\Non the circumstances...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.73,0:12:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,No guarantees.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.40,0:12:25.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, if it's {\i1}not{\i0} fun,\Nyou can do something to {\i1}make{\i0} it fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.61,0:12:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Now you're being unreasonable.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.98,0:12:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's just enjoy ourselves, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.90,0:12:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.36,0:12:33.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.61,0:12:37.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.98,0:12:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, here goes!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.44,0:12:45.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Go on, drink up!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.69,0:12:47.23,Default,,0,0,0,,How is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.11,0:12:52.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Like a soft drink, but also... not.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.94,0:12:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Does it taste good or what?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.48,0:12:59.65,Default,,0,0,0,,There's this, like,\Nburning in my throat. Deep inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.65,0:13:01.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Alcohol will do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.44,0:13:03.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What's beer like?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.48,0:13:05.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Want to try?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.07,0:13:06.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.86,0:13:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry for the wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.48,0:13:10.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Enjoy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.82,0:13:13.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Give that a taste.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.69,0:13:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.40,0:13:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.57,0:13:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,So this is beer! It's bitter,\Nbut there's more to it than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.90,0:13:27.57,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why it goes so great\Nwith fried and salty food!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.57,0:13:30.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.44,0:13:32.19,Default,,0,0,0,,So juicy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.19,0:13:34.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Now take a slug of beer.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.11,0:13:39.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Right? Isn't that delicious?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.86,0:13:41.69,Default,,0,0,0,,They go {\i1}fantastic{\i0} together!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.69,0:13:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,The beer resets the grease from the chicken\Nfor fresh new flavor with every bite!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.40,0:13:51.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, you really chugged it.\NSo what's your verdict?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.03,0:13:55.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It's {\i1}great{\i0} ! So you drink alcohol with food, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.98,0:13:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Some people savor it on its own.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.11,0:14:02.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't matter as long\Nas you're enjoying yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.86,0:14:07.07,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case, as you so kindly suggested,\NI'm gonna do just that!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.07,0:14:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right--go on, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.40,0:14:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Just how much are you ordering?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.40,0:14:17.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Your wallet is already dead.{PURE FUCKING GOLD, feed me more memes -aria}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.78,0:14:20.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up! Cancel! Cancel those!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.61,0:14:23.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Hidebu!{omfg ahahahah}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.07,0:14:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Pardon me...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.40,0:14:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,No horsing around, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.40,0:14:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.65,0:14:34.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Sheesh. Quit screwing around or--
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.57,0:14:35.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yow{\i0} ! Spicy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.78,0:14:40.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs52.5\pos(709.5,618)\frz24.33}"Russian Roulette Octopus Balls"\N"Only 1 is Super Spicy!"\N"8 for ¥550"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.78,0:14:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,What {\i1}is{\i0} this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.94,0:14:40.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like one of them is ultra spicy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.82,0:14:42.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Beer! Beer!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.11,0:14:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It's empty?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.11,0:14:44.57,Default,,0,0,0,,And no water, either!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.57,0:14:46.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Uzaki, a drink! Anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.94,0:14:49.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait just a sec, okay? I'm looking.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.61,0:14:51.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I {\i1}can't{\i0} wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.11,0:14:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I bet {\i1}I{\i0} can make {\i1}this{\i0} one.\NI should make it for you sometime!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.48,0:14:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm begging you: make it snappy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.94,0:15:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I was a goner...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.28,0:15:08.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, this is good!\NI think I might like {\i1}yuzu{\i0} liqueur.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.57,0:15:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Good for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.28,0:15:15.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Another round!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.07,0:15:16.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Now wait just one minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.61,0:15:17.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.61,0:15:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You're really knocking 'em back there.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.03,0:15:23.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Take it easy--it {\i1}is{\i0} your first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.11,0:15:24.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Pardon me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.36,0:15:25.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Your {\i1}yuzu{\i0} liqueur.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.53,0:15:26.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Much obliged!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.36,0:15:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,That's {\i1}too fast{\i0} !
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.36,0:15:32.07,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm totally fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.07,0:15:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine? How many is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.82,0:15:35.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Good question.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.94,0:15:37.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it, now?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.69,0:15:41.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, whatever.\NDrink some water in there, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.11,0:15:47.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I just might be a heavyweight!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.19,0:15:50.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, just slow down, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.07,0:15:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry for the wait! Your {\i1}yuzu{\i0} liqueur.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.86,0:15:52.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.34,0:15:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yesss!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.86,0:15:58.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.19,0:16:02.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa, whoa, whoa...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.82,0:16:06.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You okay there, Senpai? You're kinda wobbly!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.07,0:16:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the only one wobbling around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.90,0:16:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,She started out okay but\Nturned out pretty much as I'd expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.90,0:16:17.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I jotted down how much you drank.\NStay under that amount next time, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.82,0:16:21.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, Senpai, you sure got tall all of a sudden.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.03,0:16:24.03,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a utility pole! Walk properly, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.03,0:16:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Aw, c'mon, Senpai, carry me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.90,0:16:30.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Let go of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.28,0:16:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Piggyback! Baby back... ribs...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.44,0:16:36.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop that! Your various...\Nareas... are all up on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.23,0:16:39.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Various areas? Whazzat mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.15,0:16:41.19,Default,,0,0,0,,What's touchin' where?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.19,0:16:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Jeez, she is one irritating drunk!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.28,0:16:45.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Smooshy...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.48,0:16:47.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Markin' you with my scent...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.57,0:16:50.65,Default,,0,0,0,,No way can I send her home on her own like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.65,0:16:52.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, stand up. I'll take you home.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.98,0:16:55.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Aw! I'm not goin' home!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.61,0:16:57.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's drink at {\i1}your{\i0} place, Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.86,0:17:00.19,Default,,0,0,0,,What, more drinking?!\NGo home and get to sleep, dummy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.19,0:17:02.82,Default,,0,0,0,,And stand up already! I can see your underwear!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.82,0:17:05.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Who're you callin' a dummy, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.53,0:17:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, Senpai, d'you know what time it is?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.90,0:17:09.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.78,0:17:11.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Yikes! That late?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.73,0:17:16.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, too bad! No more trains! Ha ha! You dummy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.61,0:17:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You're{\i0} the dummy who can't get home, dummy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.28,0:17:20.94,Default,,0,0,0,,We can call a cab.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.98,0:17:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Uzaki's dumbass drinking drained me dry!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.11,0:17:28.07,Default,,0,0,0,,The ATM should still be running.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.07,0:17:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh, but that access fee... and taxis\Nwill be charging pricey late-night fares...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.32,0:17:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Let her stay over? I could never!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.48,0:17:38.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't think straight with this booze in me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.07,0:17:40.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Quite the dilemma!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.78,0:17:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You wouldn't abandon your junior,\Nstuck away from home, would you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.53,0:17:50.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me this was\Nall calculated from the get-go!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.53,0:17:57.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't even care anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.53,0:17:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going to the convenience store.\NI want some water.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.86,0:18:03.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! And alcohol!\NI wanna verify my age! 'Cause I'm 20!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.98,0:18:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.40,0:18:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, just so you know,\NI only have one futon set.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.40,0:18:11.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Wanna sleep together?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.65,0:18:14.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm splitting it up, moron! One quilt each!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.57,0:18:22.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Senpai... Hey, Senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.61,0:18:25.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't go to sleep, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.65,0:18:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm begging you, let me sleep.\NIt's three in the morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.40,0:18:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's play a game.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.28,0:18:33.86,Default,,0,0,0,,No way. You play dirty.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.86,0:18:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Aw...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.73,0:18:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you {\i1}still{\i0} drinking?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.19,0:18:39.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.15,0:18:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Honestly... She needs to learn\Nabout the horrors of alcohol.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.40,0:18:48.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Squid's yummy...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.61,0:18:52.11,Default,,0,0,0,,No--come morning, she'll know.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.11,0:18:55.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-oh... I really am sleepy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.07,0:18:57.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine. I'll just sleep right here, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.94,0:18:57.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.90,0:19:02.11,Default,,0,0,0,,No stun-locking moves this time,\Nso let's get sparrin'!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.11,0:19:04.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Senpai? Hey, Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.82,0:19:06.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Pipe down.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.61,0:19:10.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Senpai? Are you asleep for real?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.73,0:19:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, well.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.36,0:19:15.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Leaving behind your junior\Nand just... going to sleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.11,0:19:17.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Just ignore her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.32,0:19:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe he'll wake up if I kiss him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.48,0:19:37.07,Default,,0,0,0,,See, I {\i1}knew{\i0} you were only faking!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.07,0:19:39.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't get so worked up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.40,0:19:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It was just a joke--a joke!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.73,0:19:47.15,Default,,0,0,0,,But you sure were frantic there, Senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.15,0:19:49.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you never been kissed, by any chance?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.11,0:19:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,,No! Shut up! Go to sleep, idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.78,0:20:01.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Sleepytime...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.11,0:20:11.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Aw...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.65,0:20:14.61,Default,,0,0,0,,My head hurts... I feel awful...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.61,0:20:18.11,Default,,0,0,0,,That's called a hangover.\NLife's going to suck for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.11,0:20:19.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I hate it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.98,0:20:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are {\i1}you{\i0} just fine?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.28,0:20:25.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Grown-ups drink in moderation\Nso {\i1}that{\i0} doesn't happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.69,0:20:28.19,Default,,0,0,0,,What's "modera"--
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.19,0:20:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. Everyone has an alcohol screw-up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.78,0:20:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Good thing your first time wasn't\Nat some sketchy drinking party.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.44,0:20:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not good at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.36,0:20:41.32,Default,,0,0,0,,But you found your limit right off the bat.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.23,0:20:44.19,Default,,0,0,0,,He's in lecture mode.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.19,0:20:47.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't drink much water, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.07,0:20:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It takes water to metabolize alcohol.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.48,0:20:52.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Alternate with drinks of water\Nand you won't get sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.65,0:20:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You should feel better by noon.\NJust have to tough it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.48,0:20:59.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you listening?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.28,0:21:02.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, she's in hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.44,0:21:11.94,Default,,0,0,0,,The bigger the screw-up, the better the lesson.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.94,0:21:15.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time, drink as much water as you do booze.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.15,0:21:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,'S fine. I won't drink again as long as I live.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.82,0:21:25.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Probably for the best.\NThough everyone with a hangover says that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.65,0:21:29.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Never... ever again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.82,0:21:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to hit the store--\Nyou hold down the fort.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.48,0:21:35.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Rest up, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.23,0:21:39.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.40,0:21:41.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.69,0:21:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks a lot... for being with me... at the pub.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.44,0:21:52.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It was fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.11,0:21:54.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad you enjoyed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.23,0:21:58.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I nearly forgot: You're 20 now, Uzaki--
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.11,0:22:06.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Happy birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.23,0:23:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Something's happening!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.44,0:23:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.03,0:23:50.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Sak!
